<h2>The 10 Highest-Converting Email List Building Strategies</h2>
<p>Every strategy below has been tested by real businesses. They are ranked by average conversion rate and ease of implementation.</p>
<h3>1. Lead Magnets (5 to 15% Conversion Rate)</h3>
<p>A lead magnet is something valuable you give away in exchange for an email address. The best lead magnets solve a specific problem immediately.</p>
<p><strong>What converts best in 2026:</strong></p>
